Ma Ruler》。</p><p> 《Pleasure Best》将于 12 月 1 日发行，据称记录了 Haiku Hands 核心三人组（即 Lewis 以及 Claire Nakazawa 和 Mie Nakazawa 的兄妹二人组）自 2020 年发行<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/haiku-hands-self-titled-debut-review-2749908" target="_blank" rel="noopener">首张同名专辑</a>以来的生活。</p><p>该项目以单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/haiku-hands-tease-debut-album-with-new-single-manbitch-2656131" target="_blank" rel="noopener">“Manbitch”</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sofi-tukker" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Sofi Tukker</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/haiku-hands-announce-album-with-new-song-fashion-model-art-featuring-sofi-tukker-2718312" target="_blank" rel="noopener">“Fashion Model Art”</a>为特色，在 9 月份发行后获得了<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/haiku-hands-self-titled-debut-review-2749908" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>NME</em>的四星评价</a>。 “[Haiku Hands] 的同名首秀是一种急需的欣快喜悦的爆发，它会让你觉得你可以挑战世界，” <i>NME</i>写道。</p><p> 2021 年，Haiku Hands 发行了同名首张专辑的豪华版，其中包含另外四首曲目，包括单曲“Bye Bye”和“Shoot The Shot”。今年早些时候，Haiku Hands 在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/governors-ball-2023-new-york-city-live-review-3455384" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2023 年州长舞会音乐节上</a>表演， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-odesza-kendrick-lamar-announced-to-headline-governors-ball-2023-3382282" target="_blank" rel="noopener">加入的阵容</a>还包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lil-nas-x" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Lil Nas X</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/diplo" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Diplo</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rina-sawayama" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Rina Sawayama</a>等。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/haiku-hands-announce-new-album-pleasure-best-share-latest-single-feels-so-good-3496241">Haiku Hands 宣布新专辑《Pleasure Best》后，分享最新单曲《Feels So Good》</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
